omorrow/ |title=The CW Sets Katy Keene Series Premiere Date, Plus New Seasons of Roswell and Legends of Tomorrow |last=Swift |first=Andy |work=TVLine |date=November 8, 2019 |accessdate=November 8, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191108200639/https://tvline.com/2019/11/08/cw-premiere-dates-katy-keene-roswell-legends-of-tomorrow/ |archive-date=November 8, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref> The series finale was scheduled to air on May 18, 2020, but production was delayed, due to the [[2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://tvline.com/2019/11/08/supernatural-series-finale-airdate-final-episode-season-15/ |title=Supernatural and Arrow Get Series Finale Dates at The CW |last=Gelman |first=Vlada |work=TVLine |date=November 8, 2019 |accessdate=November 8, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191108200640/https://tvline.com/2019/11/08/supernatural-series-finale-airdate-final-episode-season-15/ |archive-date=November 8, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref> This is the fourth and final season with [[Andrew Dabb]] and [[Robert Singer (producer)|Robert Singer]] as [[showrunner]]s.\n\n==Cast==\n===Starring===\n* [[Jared Padalecki]] as [[Sam Winchester]]\n* [[Jensen Ackles]] as [[Dean Winchester]]\n* [[Alexander Calvert]] as [[List of angels in Supernatural#Jack Kline|Jack Kline]] / [[List of Supernatural characters#Belphegor|Belphegor]]{{efn|Calvert is only credited for his respective episode appearances.|name=|group=}}\n* [[Misha Collins]] as [[Castiel (Supernatural)|Castiel]]{{efn|Collins is only credited for his respective episode appearances.|name=|group=}}\n\n===Special guest stars===\n* [[Jim Beaver]] as [[Bobby Singer]]\n* [[DJ Qualls]] as [[List of Supernatural characters#Garth Fitzgerald IV|Garth Fitzgerald IV]]\n\n===Guest stars===\n{{Columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Ruth Connell]] as [[List of Supernatural characters#Rowena MacLeod|Rowena MacLeod]]<ref name=\"comicbook.com\">{{cite web |url=https://comicbook.com/tv-shows/2019/09/28/supernatural-final-season-15-episode-3-synopsis/ |title=Supernatural Will Send Out an SOS in \"Raising Hell\" |website=Comicbook.com |first=Megan |last=Peters |date=September 28, 2019 |accessdate=September 28, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190930222436/https://comicbook.com/tv-shows/2019/09/28/supernatural-final-season-15-episode-3-synopsis/ |archive-date=September 30, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n* David Haydn-Jones as [[List of Supernatural characters#Arthur Ketch|Arthur Ketch]]<ref name=\"comicbook.com\"/>\n* [[Osric Chau]] as [[Kevin Tran]]<ref name=\"tvinsider\">{{cite web |url=https://www.tvinsider.com/811003/supernatural-season-15-kevin-eileen-returning/ |title='Supernatural's Final Season Will Bring Back the Winchesters' Dead Allies |website=TV Insider |first=Ileane |last=Rudolph |date=September 26, 2019 |accessdate=September 28, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190928231445/https://www.tvinsider.com/811003/supernatural-season-15-kevin-eileen-returning/ |archive-date=September 28, 2019 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n* [[Rob Benedict]] as [[List of Supernatural characters#Chuck Shurley|Chuck Shurley / God]]\n* [[Emily Swallow]] as [[List of Supernatural characters#The Darkness|Amara / The Darkness]]\n* [[Emily Perkins]] as [[List of Supernatural characters#Becky Rosen|Becky Rosen]]\n* [[Ty Olsson]] as [[List of Supernatural characters#Benny Lafitte|Benny Lafitte]]\n* Anna Grace Barlow as [[Lilith (Supernatural)|Lilith]] / Ashley Monroe\n* [[Shoshannah Stern]] as Eileen Leahy<ref name=\"tvinsider\"/>\n* [[Christian Kane]] as Lee Webb<ref>{{cite web |url=https://ew.com/tv/2019/09/30/supernatural-season-15-christian-kane-guest-star/ |title=''Angel'' alum Christian Kane to guest star on final season of ''Supernatural'' |website=Entertainment Weekly |first=Samantha |last=Highfill |date=September 30, 2019 |accessdate=October 1, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191001103350/https://ew.com/tv/2019/09/30/supernatur